settings.heading: 99% effective antibacterial
settings.description: Made from clinically-proven advanced fabric with silver ion fabric technology. Silver is a well known antimicrobial that can kill viruses and bacteria. The nylon material is coated with 99% pure silver and 1% silver oxide

settings.heading: Premium quality that keeps your face comfortable
settings.description: Thick and sturdy to make your face feel secured and well covered whilst keeping you comfortable. It’s not just your crown jewels that deserve to feel like royalty

settings.heading: Adjustable straps for extra comfort
settings.description: Not your regular one-size-fits all. We know that everyone has different sized heads so these adjustable straps allow you to find your preferred comfort zone!

settings.heading: Take care of yourself, others and the earth
settings.description: Our masks are washable and reusable. So you not only save yourself and your pocket from the hassle of buying multiple disposable masks, but you also help to reduce landfill pollution with these environmentally friendly masks.
